---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about HSL Innovations, an independent software studio building thoughtful apps for Apple platforms."
>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Thoughtful apps, built with care.</h1>
    <p>
      HSL Innovations is an independent software studio focused on building
      simple, polished, privacy-minded, and accessible apps for Apple platforms.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>About HSL Innovations</h2>
    <p>
      HSL Innovations was created to build software that feels useful, calm, and
      carefully designed. Every app is built with attention to user experience,
      accessibility, privacy, and long-term quality.
    </p>

    <p>
      The goal is simple: create apps that people enjoy using and can rely on in
      everyday life.
    </p>

    <h2>Meet the Developer</h2>
    <p>
      Hi, I'm Hassan Lindsay, the founder and developer behind HSL Innovations.
      I build apps using Swift and SwiftUI with a focus on creating polished
      experiences for iPhone and iPad.
    </p>

    <p>
      My background includes software development, public service,
      transportation, and barbering. These areas taught me leadership,
      teamwork, decision-making under pressure, and a commitment to serving
      others. Those lessons continue to influence how I design software; 
      building products that are dependable, thoughtfully crafted, and made to
      serve real people.
    </p>

    <h2>What HSL Innovations Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> Apps should be easy to understand and enjoyable to use.</li>
      <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> Users should know how their information is handled.</li>
      <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Thoughtful design should support more people.</li>
      <li><strong>Quality:</strong> Small details matter.</li>
      <li><strong>Craft:</strong> Software should feel intentional, polished, and reliable.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Current Projects</h2>
    <p>
      HSL Innovations is currently developing and supporting apps including <a href="/apps/flora">Flora Endless Word Search</a> and KickzBrary.
    </p>

    <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
    <p>
      HSL Innovations is just getting started. Future apps will continue to focus
      on thoughtful design, privacy, accessibility, and practical everyday use.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
